Text: CLE Confirmation Cc for registering to participate in the third seminar of our CLE Series for InHouse Counsel We look forward to seeing you Thursday As a reminder the following are the details WHO Featured Speaker Gregory M Hasley Akin Gump Strauss Hauer Feld LLP WHAT Can You Keep a Secret WHEN Thursday April Noon pm WHERE The Houston Club Rusk th Floor Gulf Coast Room please note that this is a room change from the previous seminars PARKING Valet parking is complimentary at the Chase Bank Building which is located at Rusk corner of Louisiana and Rusk Please bring your ticket with you to the luncheon for validation Please feel free to email me or call me at if you have any questions or need additional information Thanks Christine Campbell Marketing Manager Akin Gump Strauss Hauer Feld
